Here's How to Pair:

Step 1: Download Samsung Gear App from Google Playstore to your phone. For non-Samsung phone user, please also download Samsung Accessory Service and Gear S Plugin Apps.

Step 2: Launch Samsung Gear App on your phone. Go to "SETTINGS" Tab and choose Samsung Galaxy App. Then search and download eGeeTouch Manager App. 

Step 3: Launch eGeeTouch App on your phone to connect with eGeeTouch lock.

Step 4: Launch eGeeTouch App on the watch. 

The smart lock will automatically connect with your phone and watch.
